entry.def: To export products or raw materials means to sell them to another country.

example.ex: They expect the antibiotic products to be exported to Southeast Asia and Africa...
example.tran: 他们希望向东南亚和非洲出口抗生素产品。

entry.def: Exports are goods which are sold to another country and sent there.

example.ex: He did this to promote American exports...
example.tran: 他这么做是为了推广美国出口产品。

entry.def: To export something means to introduce it into another country or make it happen there.

example.ex: It has exported inflation at times.
